reviewText: I LOVED IT AND THE PRICE, TOO..
was a ok kind of film but will not watch again....

It was also very odd to see the nude scene with Sasha Montenegro was edited out. I almost crapped my pants when I saw that was cut. I've seen the vhs of this back in the 80s and 90s, so I know there was something weird going on. Still, the second vignette is left pretty much intact. Isaura Espinoza wasn't bad looking back then. Recommended only for those who want to hit paydirt in the Mexican sexy comedy genre.
